<body><div class=WordSection1>
<div class="brand">📚 ENGLISH CODING · 영어코딩</div>
<h1>🌀 M002 Week 1 — While Loop</h1>
<p><strong>Topic:</strong> Repeat Until a Wall · <strong>Course:</strong> Maze Madness · <strong>Level:</strong> Intermediate · <strong>Time:</strong> about 35 minutes</p>
<p>A while loop checks first, then moves. It stops at a wall.</p>
<hr />
<h2>1 · Trace It 🔮</h2>
<pre><code>while no wall ahead:
    move forward
</code></pre>
<p><strong>The wall is 4 steps away. How many times does the agent move?</strong></p>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

<hr />
<h2>2 · Real Code 🤖</h2>
<pre><code>while not agent.detect(BLOCK, FORWARD):
    agent.move(FORWARD, 1)
</code></pre>
<p><code>agent.detect(BLOCK, FORWARD)</code> is true when a wall is ahead.</p>
<p><strong>Fill the blanks:</strong></p>
<pre><code>while not agent.detect(BLOCK, ____):
    agent.____(FORWARD, 1)
</code></pre>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

<hr />
<h2>3 · Fix the Bug 🐛</h2>
<p>The agent should move until the wall. This is backwards.</p>
<pre><code>while agent.detect(BLOCK, FORWARD):
    agent.move(FORWARD, 1)
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Write the fix:</strong></p>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

<hr />
<h2>4 · Write It ✏️</h2>
<p>Make the agent move forward until a wall, then turn right.</p>
<blockquote>
<p>Use <code>while</code>, <code>agent.detect</code>, <code>agent.move</code>, <code>agent.turn</code>.</p>
</blockquote>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

<hr />
<h2>5 · Show Your Work 📸🎥</h2>
<p>Open your homework world. Use a while loop. Move the agent down the straight maze to the wall.</p>
<p>Record <strong>one video</strong> (a phone is fine). Show two things:</p>
<p><strong>1 · Your code.</strong> Scroll through it. Say what each part does.</p>
<p><strong>2 · Your build.</strong> Point the camera. Name the parts.</p>
<p>Fill the blanks:</p>
<blockquote>
<p>Today I built ______.</p>
<p>I built it using this code: ______.</p>
<p>In this code I used ______.</p>
<p>The hardest part was ______.</p>
<p>That part was hard because ______.</p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>Write your lines here, then say them in your video.</strong></p>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

